dct_title_s: Rutgers University, New Jersey 1934 Queens Campus study
dct_description_sm: An architectural and landscape study for Rutgers University, New Brunswick, New Jersey preliminary study for Queens Campus and Neilson Campus with suggestions for new buildings and student walks. Includes a directory of existing campus buildings and drawings of proposed buildings. Existing vegetation is also depicted.
